## Deployment
The app is deployed on **Render** and can be accessed at: [https://savemom.onrender.com/](https://savemom.onrender.com/)

To deploy manually:
```sh
npm run build
npm run start
```

## Future Improvements
- Backend API integration for real-time appointment data.
- Authentication & user roles.
- Dark mode support.
- Improved UI animations and accessibility features.

